# ERP API - User CRUD Operations

## Base URL
http://localhost:5162

## Endpoints

### 1. Get All Users
GET {{base}}/api/auth/users
Content-Type: application/json

### 2. Get User by ID
GET {{base}}/api/auth/users/{{userId}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 3. Create User
POST {{base}}/api/auth/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "test@example.com",
    "password": "password123",
    "image": "profile.jpg",
    "phone": "+1234567890",
    "typeUser": "Admin"
}

### 4. Update User
PUT {{base}}/api/auth/users/{{userId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "image": "new-profile.jpg",
    "phone": "+0987654321",
    "typeUser": "User"
}

### 5. Delete User
DELETE {{base}}/api/auth/users/{{userId}}
Content-Type: application/json

# Variables
@base = http://localhost:5162
@userId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
